Detailed Description

GENERATED CLASS.

Represents the <display-string> XML element in memory. DTD declaration:

 <!ELEMENT display-string EMPTY>
 <!ATTLIST display-string
      value               CDATA     IMPLIED
      banner-comment      CDATA     IMPLIED
      right-comment       CDATA     "&#10;" >
